</img>
 
<p>  </p>
<p>Digital publishing gives me access, flexibility, and the freedom to revise <br>
as I learn. It also gives my work a chance to connect with people I may never <br> 
meet. Publishing turns my ideas into something that can travel, be found, and <br>
maybe matter to someone else.That possibility is why it feels significant. </p>

